description: Information about the data that is collected for the specified assessment run.

parameters.name: assessmentRunArn
parameters.description: The ARN that specifies the assessment run that has the telemetry data that you want to obtain.

nested_items.name: messageType
nested_items.description: A specific type of behavioral data that is collected by the agent.

nested_items.name: count
nested_items.description: The count of messages that the agent sends to the Amazon Inspector service.

nested_items.name: dataSize
nested_items.description: The data size of messages that the agent sends to the Amazon Inspector service.
